						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pedestal of the image of Ādinātha-tīrthaṅkara.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1445.</p>						

						<p>This damaged record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka [13]66, Raktākshi, Māgha, ba., Sunday,</hi> the <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> being not given. The intended date may be <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1445, January 24 or 31, Sunday.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription seems to record the installation of the image of Ādinātha.</p>						

						</summary>
